          About Myself
        </h1>
        <p class="description mb-4">
          I've been programming websites and web-apps
          for the past five years.
          I’ve achieved frontend, backend,
          and architecture skills, being able
          to build a variety of web applications
          following criteria of robustness,
          security, and scalability. <br> <br>

          I’m an organized, detail-oriented,
          self-motivated, and dedicated
          professional, able to build products
          without constant supervision.
          I’m a passionate professional and
          I seek a deep understanding of
          client businesses to raise relevant
          suggestions and help with their
          interests as a whole.

        </p>
        <p class="text-uppercase primary mb-4">Let's connect</p>
        <div class="d-inline-flex flex-wrap">
          <a target="_blank" href="https://twitter.com/DavidYao3">
            <i class="fab fa-twitter m-2"></i>
          </a>
          <a target="_blank" href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/david-yao-armel/?locale=en_US">
            <i class="fab fa-linkedin-in m-2"></i>
          </a>
          <a target="_blank" href="https://github.com/daviidy">
            <i class="fab fa-github m-2"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
        <div>
          <button href="#" class="project-cta p-2">
